/knowledge_tree.db

# Per-machine editor state when data/wiki is opened as an Obsidian vault
data/.obsidian/

# Generated wiki artifacts — rebuilt on demand. Curated content under
# data/wiki/papers and data/wiki/concepts stays tracked.
data/wiki/index.md
data/wiki/lint-report.md
data/wiki/decks/
data/wiki/reports/

# Logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
